From e3f39753ad57e2bd48493c4912d77d796f211596 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mykyta Diachyna <m.diachyna@inango-systems.com>
Date: Thu, 11 Sep 2025 16:33:24 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] miniupnpd: upnpsoap: Add MAC-based permissions

Add MAC-based permissions in order to identify
control points not only by IP, but also by MAC

References: PCF-1999
Signed-off-by: Mykyta Diachyna <m.diachyna@inango-systems.com>
